    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="起因"><a href="#起因" class="headerlink" title="起因"></a>起因</h2><p>最近被🐏了个🐏刷屏了</p><p>正好看见<a href="https://yupi.icu/">鱼皮</a>出了个低配版</p><p>那必须整起来!</p><h2 id="经过"><a href="#经过" class="headerlink" title="经过"></a>经过</h2><p>####1.首先clone下来</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/liyupi/yulegeyu.git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>####2.打开VS code</p><p>####3.下载依赖</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>不过我下载的有点慢,不知道是不是我的问题</p><p>####4.生成静态文件</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm run build</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>####5.运行</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm run dev</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>####6.如图所示</p><p><img src="https://npm.elemecdn.com/marcusyyds-assets@1.0.4/img/20220917210044.jpg">)</p><h2 id="写在最后"><a href="#写在最后" class="headerlink" title="写在最后"></a>写在最后</h2><p>如果有错误</p><p>望纠正(勿喷)</p><p>来<a href="https://akilar.top/">店长</a>群里<del>玩呀</del>请教大佬 </p><p><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2022/09/17/63255541c9b4a.jpg" alt="QQ群"></p>]]></content>
    
    
